OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F466A1715707699
OL,3,CWoman first ever to give British Sign
OL,4,CLanguage speech at Buckingham Palace
OL,6,F"Deaf people can do anything hearing
OL,7,Fpeople can do, except hear. We may
OL,8,Fcommunicate in a different language,
OL,9,Fbut we are still able to communicate.
OL,11,F"For my volunteering section, I chose
OL,12,Fto teach other people BSL. I want to
OL,13,Fraise awareness of BSL and encourage
OL,14,Feveryone to learn just a little bit
OL,15,Fbecause it means deaf BSL users will
OL,16,Fhave less anxiety in the community."
OL,18,FNow a Duke of Edinburgh ambassador in
OL,19,FWales, Ms Clarke said she wants to be
OL,20,F"a voice for young people with
OL,21,Fdisabilities."
