OL,6,FParticipants have to complete 12
OL,7,Fmonths of volunteering, a four-day
OL,8,Fexpedition and various other
OL,9,Fchallenges, including a residential
OL,10,Ftrip, to receive a gold award.
OL,12,FTalking about the confidence the
OL,13,Fcourse has given her, Ms Clarke added:
OL,14,F"Duke of Edinburgh taught me that if
OL,15,Fthe skies get rough, I won't give up
OL,16,For let my deafness stop me. Thank you
OL,17,FDuke of Edinburgh for making me feel
OL,18,Fhappy, proud and ready for anything."
