OL,6,FShe told PA news agency she was "lost
OL,7,Ffor words" whilst talking to Prince
OL,8,FEdward, who is the Duke of Edinburgh
OL,9,Fand the youngest brother of King
OL,10,FCharles.
OL,12,FCongratulating the audience on their
OL,13,Fawards, the Duke of Edinburgh said: "
OL,14,F"I hope on the whole the experience of
OL,15,Fdoing your award was a good one."
OL,17,FJokingly, he added: "I'm pretty sure
OL,18,Fthat there were moments when you were
OL,19,Fwondering why you were doing it.
