OL,6,F"And if it was anything like doing
OL,7,Fmine, it was about halfway through in
OL,8,Fthe expedition."
OL,10,FAstronaut Tim Peake was amongst those
OL,11,Fto also speak at the event.
OL,13,FHe drew a parallel between his time in
OL,14,Fspace and the Duke of Edinburgh award,
OL,15,Fwith an emergency during a spacewalk
OL,16,Frequiring "teamwork, communication and
OL,17,Ffollowership," the same skills people
OL,18,Fhad "been honing" through the award.
